<div class="container">
    <h1>About</h1>
</div>

<div>
    <h4> Purpose </h4>
    <p>
        -This site was designed to allow you to track your past expenditures/income in order to help you plan for the future
    </p>
    <p>
        -Life is too short to spend at work. Our goal is to see everyone achieve financial indepdence as quick as they can
    </p>
    <p>
    -The more money you have, the more pizza you can have (just saying)
    </p>
</div>

<br>
</br>

<!-- Button trigger modal -->
<div id = "bootstrap-button">
    <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#exampleModal">
        How it works
    </button>
</div>


<!-- Modal -->
<div class="modal fade" id="exampleModal" tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="exampleModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
  <div class="modal-dialog">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <div class="modal-header">
        <h5 class="modal-title" id="exampleModalLabel">How it works</h5>
        <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-body">
        <p>
            -Sign up -> Start entering your past data (use your bank/credit card statements to find your expenses)
        </p>
        <p>
            -Evaluate the past data -> what areas surpise you? Where are you spending more money than you thought?
        </p>
        <p>
            -Enter future data -> give your best guess (using the past data as a model) to your upcoming income/expenses
        </p>
        <p>
            -Evaluate the future data -> are you able to pay all your bills? If so, great! Start planning how much you can save/where those savings dollars will go
        </p>
        <p>
            -Evaluate the future data -> are you able to pay all your bills? If not, no big deal! Start planning what expenses you can eliminate and/or how you can earn more money
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-footer">
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-bs-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<br>
